    "swelling_study": {
        "description": "Swelling studies performed in distilled water at room temperature. Results shown in Figure 1. HPMC formulations showed highest hydration ability, followed by Kollidon SR, then Ethocel. Swelling increased with polymer concentration and with higher viscosity grade (K100M > K4M).",
        "data_table": "See figure_1_hydration_data"
    },
