    },
    "conclusion": "Controlled release tizanidine HCl tablets successfully prepared with HPMC K4M (50%), HPMC K100M (40%), Ethocel 10FP (40%), and Kollidon SR (55%). Formulation K100M9 (HPMC K100M 40%) was best with highest shelf life (30.35 months) and zero-order release kinetics via anomalous transport."
}